{"tid":218567,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本土研究社香港前途研究計劃，超過200份解密檔案，現接受報名！","createTime":"2017-04-26T15:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T11:33:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71c7fbff9547d8a7c751ce58b4cc4be291227fa6","tid":218567,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"檔案研究，正式啟動﹗<br />\n【建檔偉業－香港前途談判檔案共讀計劃】<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/2ik1EGNDilQ4xrXj2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F2ik1EGNDilQ4xrXj2&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=3406359b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/2ik1EGNDilQ4xrXj2</a><br />\n<br />\n香港前途研究計劃正式開始！過去數月，我們在英國倫敦搜集了超過200份解密檔案，由於數量龐大，現希望廣招朋友一起閱讀有關香港前途談判過程的檔案，重組整個中英談判過程的內容，齊齊為香港歷史解密。<br />\n<br />\n預期成果：<br />\n1. 一起重構「香港前途談判時間廊」(timeline)，詳細疏理1979年至1984年中英談判細節；<br />\n2. 發掘當中的關鍵事件、人物等，並將其帶到現今社會脈絡討論。<br />\n<br />\n招募對象：<br />\n᪀ 關心香港歷史及前途問題<br />\n᪀ 有興趣閱讀英國政府解密檔案<br />\n᪂ 有興趣參與協作式研究<br />\n᪂ 沒有患上民族主義幼稚病<br />\n<br />\n計劃安排：<br />\n在5月6日前閱讀及整理獲派發的解密檔案，並參與共讀會議，討論習得內容；<br />\n第一次共讀會議<br />\n日期：2017年5月6日（星期六）<br />\n時間：10am- 5pm (午膳時間：1pm-2:30pm）<br />\n地點：香港中文大學<br />\n<br />\n第二次共讀：待定<br />\n<br />\n費用：全免（包免費午餐）<br />\n<br />\n報名及詳情：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/2ik1EGNDilQ4xrXj2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F2ik1EGNDilQ4xrXj2&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=3406359b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/2ik1EGNDilQ4xrXj2</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n「香港前途研究計劃」眾籌：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/nAxsfr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnAxsfr&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=6ed4a33b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/nAxsfr</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063.72534.244689185627162/1424046614358074/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063.72534.244689185627162%2F1424046614358074%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=76edecd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063.72534.244689185627162/1424046614358074/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"3fa2d5458e55a89de95e25ecc31fd6a87934ff4f","tid":218567,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"沒有患上民族主義幼稚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738901b881ac28b4a64427ad931a570b41853438","tid":218567,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒有患上民族主義幼稚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊黃之峰"},{"pid":"616188f3526e98a34496f025ab792fede62986fa","tid":218567,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fcd17a63799c174d42b76932179b6c3d124a0b","tid":218567,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沒有患上民族主義幼稚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊黃之峰</blockquote><br />\n其實咩黎，有冇仔細定義"},{"pid":"056d94877573986a6528e8b9ef6fed289f265b1d","tid":218567,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沒有患上民族主義幼稚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><